	   <tr><td colspan=2>Troll SK or an Ogre SK?&nbsp;&nbsp;I've been playing EQ for a long time (2 years).. I've played on 2 different Servers mainly. Eci as a wizard and MT as a warrior and shaman.  All are 55+ currently.  <br><br>Ive been debating creating a new character, a Shadowknight.  But, I just can't decide what race I really want to be... troll or ogre.  Iksar's to me are out of the question, simply b/c I think they look horrible.  No offence, just a personal opinion.  Also, I wish to be a large race for the Slam aspect of their races.  So that leaves out Human, DE, Erud, etc.  Leaving only Troll and Ogre.<br><br>It would appear an obvious choice.  Be a Troll for REGEN stupid.  But, I still am not certain this is as simply as that.  I am curious to hear from both Troll and Ogre SK's who have imput on this situation/question.  I have certain ideas of what benifits from either would be such as Regen on trolls and/or higher strength and stamina (more hitpoints) as an Ogre.  The no stun in front feature is also a nice trait on Ogres (if im correct on that atleast).<br><br>Please post thoughts and points to support or reject my idea of the differences between the races.  I am fairly deadlocked on choosing a race for my new character and I am hoping this will give me a better idea which of the two I want to spend some serious time playing and leveling. Thanks in advance if you answer with helpful suggestions.<br>  -- Confused future SK<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
