	   <tr><td colspan=2>I've got an ogre SK as my first character and I never noticed the benfits until I played another character.&nbsp;&nbsp;No-stun from the front is a huge benefit, since you WILL be a tank.  Then there is that ability to bash and carry tons of things.  Sure, trolls have regen and that helps when you are soloing, but sooner or later you will group.  Once there, the healer should be able to take care of that for you.  Anyway, you can't go wrong, but I love my SK ogre.<br>-Bruklin, Prexus <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
